388
00:28:11.770 --> 00:28:13.310
¿Crema batida?

389
00:28:13.310 --> 00:28:15.760
¡Nos arrastrará!

390
00:28:20.560 --> 00:28:21.720
¿Esto es...?

391
00:28:21.720 --> 00:28:22.820
