405
00:29:23.980 --> 00:29:28.480
Mi pastel de bodas...

406
00:29:28.480 --> 00:29:31.680
Pastel...

407
00:29:33.890 --> 00:29:35.530
¿Estás bien?

408
00:29:35.530 --> 00:29:36.810
¡Ayúdenme!

409
00:29:36.810 --> 00:29:37.890
¡Bien!

410
00:29:37.890 --> 00:29:39.690
